name: "Invasion of the Junkiddos"
description: Xmas excitement began to surround the entire Junkland. A special entertainment area was being planned for the little Junkkidos. But what is that! All the children who heard the news suddenly flocked to the area and made a mess. With extreme happiness and excitement, they started playing, scattering all the decorations, balloons and confetti. Although it was a mess, it was fun to see the happiness of the children.
